OL,3,CTaipei City Zoo receives a pair of red
OL,4,Cpandas from China
OL,6,FA zoo in Taiwan's capital received a
OL,7,Fpair of endangered red pandas from
OL,8,FChina on Saturday, in the first
OL,9,Fexchange of animals in more than a
OL,10,Fdecade as tensions between the two
OL,11,Fsides run high.
OL,13,FThe pandas, a three-year-old male and
OL,14,Fa two-year-old female, will be in
OL,15,Fquarantine for a month and then
OL,16,Facclimated to their new home in the
OL,17,FTaipei City Zoo before they are
OL,18,Funveiled to the public.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/4
