OL,3,CTaipei City Zoo receives a pair of red
OL,4,Cpandas from China
OL,6,FWhile tensions between China and
OL,7,FTaiwan, the self-ruled island that
OL,8,FBeijing claims as part of its
OL,9,Fterritory, remain high and official
OL,10,Fcontacts between the two governments
OL,11,Fare cut off, city-level exchanges have
OL,12,Fcontinued.
